        "line_in_english": "Once, I feared being tainted by calamity and sealed myself away. When I awoke again, this sea had been purified by my power, yet I could not undo this seal... Only you, the traveler who heard my song... Only you can help me... So, please save me~!"
      }
    ],
    "Additional_description_in_Chinese": "冈依沙瓦号是飓风阵营的超稀有风帆主力舰。她热爱香料，喜欢在料理中加入各种香料，也喜欢收集各种珍宝，虽然她自己也记不清仓库里都有什么了。她对指挥官非常热情友好，希望能和指挥官一起去各地冒险，收集更多的\"纪念品\"。换装'被封印的美人鱼'则展现了她神秘和略带诱惑的一面，声称只有指挥官能解开她的封印。",
    "Additional_description_in_english": "Ganj-i-Sawai is an Super Rare main fleet sailing ship from the Tempesta faction. She loves spices and enjoys adding various spices to her cooking. She also likes to collect all kinds of treasures, although she herself can't remember everything in her warehouse. She is very enthusiastic and friendly towards the Commander, hoping to go on adventures with the Commander to various places and collect more 'souvenirs'. Her 'Sealed Mermaid' skin shows a mysterious and slightly seductive side, claiming that only the Commander can break her seal.",
